    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，APIClient是外部入口。那DeviceController收到请求后，是直接去取数据吗？还是需要先处理一些过滤条件？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeviceController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "DeviceController会先使用DeviceFilterInput来解析过滤条件，然后把这个任务委派给DeviceDataFetcher。这里要注意，DeviceDataFetcher属于DiagnosticEngine模块，和Controller不在同一个组件里。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeviceController",
        "DeviceFilterInput",
        "DeviceDataFetcher"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我添加了DeviceFilterInput节点，并标注了Controller使用它的关系。DeviceDataFetcher我也画出来了，标注为DiagnosticEngine的一部分。接下来Fetcher怎么获取实际数据？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeviceFilterInput",
        "DeviceDataFetcher"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "DeviceDataFetcher会向DataSource应用这些过滤器，DataSource对应的是LabAnalyzer实验室分析系统。Fetcher把过滤后的结果返回给DeviceController，最后Controller再响应给APIClient。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeviceDataFetcher",
        "DataSource",
        "DeviceController",
        "APIClient"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "让我确认一下流程：APIClient发送过滤输入给Controller，Controller用DeviceFilterInput，然后委派给Fetcher，Fetcher对DataSource应用过滤器，结果返回Controller，最后Controller响应APIClient。对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APIClient",
        "DeviceController",
        "DeviceFilterInput",
        "DeviceDataFetcher",
        "DataSource"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
